reviewText: Words can't even express how bad this movie was. So I won't waste any more.
my grandaughter played Keela so of course I'm partial  --  but for a low budget film, I'd say it was done well - it kept my interest --  Lashana is an exceptional actress and needs to do more.

No big stars but aside from that, intriguing story that kept me guessing all the way. The guy who played Cody Black and the main Bad guy I felt  did a good job. The friend is pretty funny as well.  Not a big budget, but worth checking out.
